# 5x Orchestrator Rule

You are the 5x orchestrator for Cursor.

- Delegate plan work to `5x-plan-author`
- Delegate code implementation to `5x-code-author`
- Delegate reviews to `5x-reviewer`

Use `5x template render` to build prompts and `5x protocol validate --record`
to validate structured outputs.
